#: 02701:9
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Oh! Hi, Kazushi-kun!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:11
msgid "I saw Haruka running towards me as I was on my way to the girls' dorm."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:14
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What a coincidence! I was just thinking about coming to see you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:18
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"You were on your way to visit me? How funny that we've met halfway!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:19
msgid "I couldn't help but cheer up as I saw her getting all excited by the prospect of my visit."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:20
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You're giving me the wrong impression.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:23
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Wrong impression? What wrong impression?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:24
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"It's nothing.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:25
msgid "I wonder if she harbors any special feelings for me."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:26
msgid "I doubt it. She's equally nice to everyone, and treats them the same. That's one of her best traits."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:27
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Are you free? Would you like to go for a walk?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:28
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Don't say that first. I was about to invite you for one.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:31
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"You were going to ask me out for a walk? I missed my chance at being asked out!!! Uwaa! Can you ask me now?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:32
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You want me to ask you now? Ok...... \n"
"Do you want to take a walk with me?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:35
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Sure!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:36
msgid "She gave me a big smile as she started walking."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:37
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Hurry up, Kazushi-kun, or I'm going to leave you behind!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:39
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Hold on.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:42
msgid "I chased after Haruka as she walked towards a beautiful full moon."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:46
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"It's scary here at night.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:47
msgid "We definitely stayed in the classroom last night. I just hadn't thought much of it with everyone there."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:48
msgid "I just hadn't thought much of it with everyone there."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:51
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"I'm so relieved that everything turned out fine last night.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:52
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Me too. It's because we all worked at it together.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:55
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"You're right. I'm just happy that everyone's finally getting along well.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:56
msgid "Her smile had put smiles on everyone else's faces. However, it disappeared the very next moment."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:59
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"I still don't understand why grandma did such a...\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:60
msgid "She was mumbling to herself as she looked down at the ground. I could barely hear her."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:61
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You mean last night? What about your grandma?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:64
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"It's nothing. I was just talking to myself.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:65
msgid "She's clearly dodging the issue. Haruka's never shown herself to be a good liar."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:66
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"If there's ever, ever anything troubling you, you know you can talk to me, right?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:67
msgid ""
"I didn't want to force her into talking...\n"
"But I truly wanted to be of help to her if she needed me."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:70
msgid "Haruka looked into my eyes."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:71
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Thanks.\n"
"I'm OK now, but if I ever need your help I'll come and find you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:72
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You do that. I'll do everything I can for you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:75
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"You're making me blush.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:76
msgid "She's smiling again. Her smile makes me feel safe for some reason."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:77
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"You do the same, OK, Kazushi-kun? I'll do everything I can to help you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:78
msgid "Her pure smile touched my heart."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:79
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You're going to protect me?\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:82
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Of course I will! Whenever you need me, I'll be there.\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:83
msgid "I felt a sense of commitment and dedication in her words..."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:84
msgid "As if she knew something was going to happen......"
msgstr ""

#: 02701:87
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Summer break is just around the corner. We're gonna have so much fun!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:88
msgid "She started smiling again."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:89
msgid "I couldn't help but smile back at her."
msgstr ""

#: 02701:90
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Yup! We're gonna rock till we drop!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:91
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"We will!\""
msgstr ""

#: 02701:92
msgid "I have a feeling this summer is going to be very different from my previous ones. I can't wait."
msgstr ""
